Totspot,is,a,service,that,allows,parents,to,make,private,websites,for,their,children,and,share,the,website,with,friends,and,family,The,private,websites,allow,for,video,and,photo,sharing,sharing,milestones,in,the,child,s,life,and,other,content,related,to,their,child,s,life,The,Totspot,API,provides,a,way,for,developers,to,build,applications,and,other,functions,on,top,of,the,Totspot,website,Examples,of,data,the,API,can,call,include,timelines,photos,videos,and,user,information